1
00:00:50,320 --> 00:00:51,719
My father is alive!

2
00:00:52,880 --> 00:00:53,719
Who dares to offer incense?

3
00:00:54,479 --> 00:00:55,960
I saw it with my own eyes,

4
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:58,399
A'Lang was being chased by bandits!

5
00:00:58,560 --> 00:00:59,799
Yin Shifeng's actions were too conspicuous,

6
00:01:00,240 --> 00:01:01,880
which attracted the bandits' attention.

7
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,759
Now he's dead with no remains.

8
00:01:03,880 --> 00:01:05,000
It's all his own fault.

9
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:06,719
If he's alive, we want to see him.

10
00:01:07,519 --> 00:01:08,959
If he's dead, we want to see his body.

11
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,439
How can you all jump to conclusions?

12
00:01:11,640 --> 00:01:13,640
Your father borrowed 300 strings from me.

13
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:15,519
If you don't pay it back for him,

14
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:16,719
you're just a useless

15
00:01:16,959 --> 00:01:18,000
little girl.

16
00:01:18,280 --> 00:01:18,640
Why don't you

17
00:01:18,680 --> 00:01:19,799
hand over this house to me?

18
00:01:20,159 --> 00:01:21,799
I'll take care of everything for you.

19
00:01:21,799 --> 00:01:22,480
Don't you dream about it.

20
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,280
The 300 strings haven't been settled yet.

21
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:26,359
This house should be mine.

22
00:01:26,359 --> 00:01:27,000
It's yours?

23
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:28,719
It's mine!

24
00:01:28,719 --> 00:01:30,239
It's not your turn.

25
00:01:30,239 --> 00:01:31,159
It's my turn!

26
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:43,799
You can't even think about

27
00:01:45,239 --> 00:01:46,879
my Xiao family's things.

28
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:53,079
Xiao

29
00:01:54,359 --> 00:01:54,879
Jing

30
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:56,079
Yi.

31
00:02:00,760 --> 00:02:01,920
[Isn't this Chang'an's top merchant,]

32
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,000
[Xiao family's young master?]

33
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:06,120
I heard they've never been on good terms.

34
00:02:06,239 --> 00:02:08,680
What does this have to do with the Xiao family?

35
00:02:09,240 --> 00:02:11,080
Yin Shifeng has mortgaged all the Yin family's property

36
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,400
to the Xiao family.

37
00:02:12,759 --> 00:02:14,280
This deed is the proof.

38
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:16,039
Yin Xinyue,

39
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:17,680
everything here,

40
00:02:18,479 --> 00:02:19,360
including you,

41
00:02:20,080 --> 00:02:21,759
will be at my disposal from now on.

42
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,280
Take her away.

43
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:25,879
I'll go with you.

44
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:46,479
Three months.

45
00:02:47,759 --> 00:02:48,520
I'll pay off my father's debt

46
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:51,159
in three months.

47
00:02:53,080 --> 00:02:53,800
I hope

48
00:02:54,919 --> 00:02:56,240
you'll show mercy.

49
00:02:56,800 --> 00:02:58,360
Don't give away our ancestral home

50
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,280
to someone else.

51
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,199
It's been seven years.

52
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:20,360
I never thought

53
00:03:21,120 --> 00:03:23,680
we'd meet like this.

54
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:26,280
Yunzhou.

55
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,599
Marry

56
00:03:28,439 --> 00:03:30,400
a girl from the Yin Family?

57
00:03:31,080 --> 00:03:31,680
Why?

58
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,360
If it weren't for Yin Shifeng,

59
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,159
how would you...

60
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:37,599
Do as I say.

61
00:04:01,800 --> 00:04:02,919
Use your skills

62
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:04,840
to earn a living and repay the debt.

63
00:04:07,199 --> 00:04:08,639
Now that my father's whereabouts are unknown,

64
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:10,199
I must repay the debt as soon as possible

65
00:04:10,400 --> 00:04:11,240
to keep the Yin Mansion.

66
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,400
[There isn't]

67
00:04:13,639 --> 00:04:14,840
[a women's clinic in Chang'an yet.]

68
00:04:15,599 --> 00:04:16,560
[This could be my chance.]

69
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:33,480
Excuse me,

70
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:35,439
is this shop for rent?

71
00:04:39,319 --> 00:04:39,759
Come on.

72
00:04:50,399 --> 00:04:51,439
It's an epileptic seizure.

73
00:04:55,240 --> 00:04:55,879
Zhen.

74
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:57,600
Stop!

75
00:04:57,759 --> 00:04:58,639
She's about to give birth.

76
00:04:59,319 --> 00:04:59,959
If she has a seizure,

77
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:00,600
it'll be even worse.

78
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:01,279
I can handle it.

79
00:05:05,079 --> 00:05:05,800
Can you afford

80
00:05:06,120 --> 00:05:06,920
the consequences if something goes wrong?

81
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,839
This is a matter of life and death.

82
00:05:08,120 --> 00:05:09,279
The worst thing about seizures is delay.

83
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,959
If she doesn't wake up within half an incense,

84
00:05:11,199 --> 00:05:12,279
even if a healer arrives,

85
00:05:12,519 --> 00:05:13,120
her child

86
00:05:13,120 --> 00:05:14,000
will be stillborn.

87
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:18,480
Trust me.

88
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:32,639
Zhen.

89
00:05:33,879 --> 00:05:34,839
Are you feeling any better?

90
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:41,160
How is she?

91
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:45,480
Thank you for saving my life.

92
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:47,560
Here.

93
00:05:47,959 --> 00:05:48,839
Thank you, my lord.

94
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:51,800
I'm sorry.

95
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:53,000
Please forgive me.

96
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:54,920
I shouldn't have doubted you.

97
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:57,120
I almost harmed her.

98
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:00,639
You were just eager to help.

99
00:06:01,079 --> 00:06:02,079
There's no right or wrong.

100
00:06:03,879 --> 00:06:04,720
Lady,

101
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:07,079
are you here to rent a shop?

102
00:06:07,639 --> 00:06:07,959
Yes.

103
00:06:08,639 --> 00:06:09,399
I wonder

104
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:10,959
how much the rent is.

105
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:13,560
This is the proprietress.

106
00:06:13,959 --> 00:06:15,040
You can ask her.

107
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:17,079
Since you saved Zhen,

108
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:18,839
we won't deceive you.

109
00:06:19,439 --> 00:06:20,279
The men in this shop

110
00:06:20,279 --> 00:06:21,439
have all gone to defend the border.

111
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,199
What's left

112
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,319
are mostly women and children.

113
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,399
I'm afraid we can't do business.

114
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:27,759
Women and children?

115
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:32,319
That's perfect.

116
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:33,680
I'll rent it.

117
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:36,000
I'll pay three months' rent in advance,

118
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,160
and then pay monthly thereafter.

119
00:06:37,439 --> 00:06:38,079
Is that alright?

120
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:41,199
Lady,

121
00:06:41,680 --> 00:06:42,720
have you thought this through?

122
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:43,600
Yes,

123
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:44,879
I want to open

124
00:06:45,319 --> 00:06:46,160
a women's clinic,

125
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:46,560
specializing in...

126
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:46,879
No way.

127
00:06:47,959 --> 00:06:48,879
If it's just any business,

128
00:06:48,879 --> 00:06:49,959
I'd rent to you without hesitation.

129
00:06:50,319 --> 00:06:50,959
But a clinic

130
00:06:51,079 --> 00:06:52,360
is a matter of life and death.

131
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,800
Women practicing medicine

132
00:06:54,079 --> 00:06:54,759
and appearing in public

133
00:06:55,439 --> 00:06:56,439
would be seen as breaking the rules.

134
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:58,000
I'm sorry.

135
00:06:58,639 --> 00:06:59,279
Even though

136
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,439
you saved Zhen,

137
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:01,959
I can't rent the shop

138
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:02,879
to you.

139
00:07:05,040 --> 00:07:06,240
I understand your concerns.

140
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:08,439
Don't rush to turn me down.

141
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:10,000
Think about it.

142
00:07:10,319 --> 00:07:11,160
I'll come back tomorrow.

143
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,000
Sir,

144
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,160
if it weren't for this lady,

145
00:07:26,959 --> 00:07:28,040
I might not

146
00:07:28,639 --> 00:07:30,120
have been able to keep this baby.

147
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:35,680
Just now,

148
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:38,240
even I couldn't easily get her to see me.

149
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,279
Let alone others.

150
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:44,560
You know how the world looks at us.

151
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:56,519
What are you drinking?

152
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,759
I'm the matriarch of this household!

153
00:08:01,639 --> 00:08:02,600
What happened?

154
00:08:03,319 --> 00:08:03,920
Shen,

155
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,240
you're here.

156
00:08:06,279 --> 00:08:07,199
Just now,

157
00:08:07,199 --> 00:08:08,319
she forced me to drink that stuff,

158
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:09,920
saying if I didn't,

159
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:11,680
I'd be punished to kneel in the shrine.

160
00:08:11,879 --> 00:08:12,759
But that's...

161
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,319
That's a fertility inhibitor!

162
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:16,959
I didn't...

163
00:08:18,439 --> 00:08:19,319
You're always out there,

164
00:08:19,319 --> 00:08:20,519
showing your face in public.

165
00:08:20,759 --> 00:08:21,639
Now you can't have children,

166
00:08:21,639 --> 00:08:23,199
and you're making a mess at home!

167
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:26,399
Why won't you listen to me?

168
00:08:27,399 --> 00:08:28,480
You're just a merchant's daughter.

169
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,279
What truth could you possibly have?

170
00:08:30,120 --> 00:08:31,199
You should stay at home,

171
00:08:31,199 --> 00:08:32,120
copying scriptures, praying,

172
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:33,480
bringing blessings to the Shen Family!

173
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,559
That's what a wife

174
00:08:35,559 --> 00:08:36,679
should do!

175
00:08:37,799 --> 00:08:38,320
Tomorrow,

176
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:40,840
I'll place the copied scriptures

177
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:42,080
in the temple.

178
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:45,720
That's more like it.

179
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:47,679
Remember,

180
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:49,320
recite one scripture daily with sincerity.

181
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:50,840
And stay out of trouble.

182
00:08:51,840 --> 00:08:52,399
Remember,

183
00:08:52,679 --> 00:08:54,399
only a virtuous woman

184
00:08:54,399 --> 00:08:55,840
deserve to be the wife of the Shen Family.

185
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:00,600
Where's the money for this month?

186
00:09:06,600 --> 00:09:07,919
Business has been slow lately.

187
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,639
This is all we have.

188
00:09:10,679 --> 00:09:12,200
Such poor performance!

189
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:21,639
Boss.

190
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:23,120
Lady Zhen.

191
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,120
Lady Yin.

192
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,080
Lady Su, you don't

193
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:30,080
look very well.

194
00:09:30,399 --> 00:09:31,120
Is there

195
00:09:31,120 --> 00:09:32,240
something wrong with your health?

196
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,799
Don't bother.

197
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,000
Miss Su,

198
00:09:36,519 --> 00:09:37,440
may I take a look?

199
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,559
Do you often

200
00:09:42,559 --> 00:09:43,639
have cold pain

201
00:09:43,919 --> 00:09:44,879
in your lower abdomen,

202
00:09:45,279 --> 00:09:46,600
soreness and coldness

203
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,720
in your lower back and knees?

204
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:55,759
Does it hurt

205
00:09:55,799 --> 00:09:56,799
when I press here?

206
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,039
Yes.

207
00:09:58,039 --> 00:09:59,200
Scanty menstruation,

208
00:09:59,799 --> 00:10:00,600
dark clots,

209
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:01,639
prolonged spotting.

210
00:10:02,519 --> 00:10:03,279
Madam Yin,

211
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,519
please don't ask too many questions.

212
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,000
Madam Su,

213
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,360
menstruation

214
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:10,840
is not

215
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,279
something to be ashamed of.

216
00:10:12,720 --> 00:10:13,600
There's no need to avoid the topic.

217
00:10:14,360 --> 00:10:15,799
Could you show me your tongue coating?

218
00:10:29,279 --> 00:10:30,320
Miss Su,

219
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:32,960
after the miscarriage,

220
00:10:33,559 --> 00:10:34,519
your uterine lining is damaged,

221
00:10:35,080 --> 00:10:35,840
with deficiency of both qi and blood,

222
00:10:36,399 --> 00:10:37,039
internal blood stasis obstruction,

223
00:10:37,399 --> 00:10:38,159
and damage to Chong and Ren meridians.

224
00:10:38,799 --> 00:10:39,679
If not properly nourished,

225
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:40,960
you may

226
00:10:42,679 --> 00:10:43,799
never conceive.

227
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:47,600
My husband has other plans.

228
00:10:50,159 --> 00:10:52,360
Please don't bother.

229
00:10:54,480 --> 00:10:55,879
Even if you have a concubine,

230
00:10:56,799 --> 00:10:58,240
don't forsake your own health

231
00:10:59,919 --> 00:11:01,320
because of others' indifference.

232
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,200
These three prescriptions

233
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,919
use medicinal food therapy

234
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:15,639
with fumigation and external application.

235
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:18,080
I'll also prepare some sitz bath medicine

236
00:11:18,759 --> 00:11:19,639
You can insert it into your private parts.

237
00:11:20,039 --> 00:11:20,399
Then...

238
00:11:32,159 --> 00:11:32,879
My lord,

239
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,679
Lady Yin wants to open a women's clinic

240
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,879
and has her eye on a teahouse in the Changle District.

241
00:11:37,559 --> 00:11:38,679
However, the lease

242
00:11:38,919 --> 00:11:39,480
is not going smoothly.

243
00:11:40,960 --> 00:11:41,279
Go,

244
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,679
find out more about this teahouse.

245
00:11:44,159 --> 00:11:44,360
Yes, my lord.

246
00:11:50,159 --> 00:11:50,960
Lady Zhen.

247
00:11:52,879 --> 00:11:53,519
Lady Yin.

248
00:11:53,519 --> 00:11:54,720
Finally, you're here, Lady Yin.

249
00:11:54,799 --> 00:11:56,480
Lady Zhen, what happened?

250
00:11:56,759 --> 00:11:57,759
Please help the boss.

251
00:11:58,519 --> 00:11:59,600
I went to deliver medicine yesterday,

252
00:11:59,759 --> 00:12:01,240
but I was blocked by Shen Yuan's men.

253
00:12:01,679 --> 00:12:03,559
Shen Yuan always cares about his face.

254
00:12:03,960 --> 00:12:05,559
Even if he mistreats Lady Su,

255
00:12:06,200 --> 00:12:06,600
he

256
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:08,039
has never done anything like

257
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:09,000
like he did yesterday.

258
00:12:09,720 --> 00:12:10,200
I'm afraid...

259
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,600
I'm afraid that my lady is in danger.

260
00:12:13,759 --> 00:12:14,399
Don't worry.

261
00:12:14,759 --> 00:12:15,279
Take your time.

262
00:12:17,279 --> 00:12:18,279
To be honest,

263
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:19,879
I'm the personal maid

264
00:12:20,039 --> 00:12:22,240
who has been with my lady since she was a child.

265
00:12:22,679 --> 00:12:23,720
Everyone thinks

266
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,320
Shen Yuan is kind

267
00:12:25,879 --> 00:12:26,919
and they are a harmonious couple.

268
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:27,919
But in fact,

269
00:12:28,879 --> 00:12:29,879
he's tyrannical and violent,

270
00:12:29,879 --> 00:12:30,759
a wolf in sheep's clothing.

271
00:12:31,039 --> 00:12:32,240
He often beats and abuses his wife.

272
00:12:32,279 --> 00:12:32,879
What?

273
00:12:33,799 --> 00:12:34,600
Madam Yin,

274
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,440
you have a compassionate heart.

275
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:39,039
Please find a way to save her.

276
00:21:22,599 --> 00:21:23,079
Head Steward.

277
00:21:24,519 --> 00:21:25,039
Head Steward.

278
00:21:26,319 --> 00:21:26,640
What's the matter?

279
00:21:26,640 --> 00:21:26,960
Head Steward,

280
00:21:27,119 --> 00:21:27,519
I'm here to bring some medicine to...

281
00:21:27,559 --> 00:21:28,359
What are you doing?

282
00:21:29,559 --> 00:21:30,480
I'm here to bring some medicine to the lady.

283
00:21:30,799 --> 00:21:31,839
Please let me in.

284
00:21:31,880 --> 00:21:32,839
We don't need more medicine.

285
00:21:33,359 --> 00:21:34,000
The lady is fine.

286
00:21:34,599 --> 00:21:35,480
Don't bother.

287
00:21:35,519 --> 00:21:35,799
Go away.

288
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:36,240
I...

289
00:21:38,119 --> 00:21:38,519
Head Steward.

290
00:21:39,279 --> 00:21:39,920
Chamberlain.

291
00:21:40,519 --> 00:21:41,160
Chamberlain.

292
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:42,839
I just come to deliver some medicine.

293
00:21:43,640 --> 00:21:44,599
Chamberlain.

294
00:24:25,000 --> 00:24:25,839
Slow down.

295
00:24:26,119 --> 00:24:26,559
Okay.

296
00:24:28,480 --> 00:24:29,960
Yan Ge, there are many people today.

297
00:24:30,480 --> 00:24:31,720
Come down and help Xin Yue with triage.

298
00:24:32,319 --> 00:24:32,759
Coming.

299
00:24:37,119 --> 00:24:37,720
Go there and line up.

300
00:24:38,200 --> 00:24:38,640
Okay.

301
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:40,000
One for surgery.

302
00:24:44,599 --> 00:24:46,319
Quack doctor!

303
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:48,559
Women doctors

304
00:24:48,559 --> 00:24:50,039
are against the natural order.

305
00:24:51,279 --> 00:24:52,920
You got what you deserved.

306
00:24:52,920 --> 00:24:54,119
Quack doctor!

307
00:24:54,839 --> 00:24:56,079
Quack doctor!

308
00:24:57,160 --> 00:24:59,000
You killed people!

309
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:00,440
Quack doctor!

310
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:01,839
You killed people!

311
00:25:02,359 --> 00:25:03,680
The Women's Clinic killed people!

312
00:25:04,480 --> 00:25:05,640
Where are the three ladies?

313
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,240
They're coming out!

314
00:25:17,319 --> 00:25:18,279
Carrying the corpse to the courtyard,

315
00:25:18,839 --> 00:25:19,759
and scattering paper money on the ground.

316
00:25:20,240 --> 00:25:22,519
Do you dare to let me examine it in public?

317
00:27:49,039 --> 00:27:49,720
Lady Zhen.

318
00:27:51,759 --> 00:27:52,559
Lady Yin.

319
00:27:53,519 --> 00:27:54,839
I came to deliver medicine to Lady Su.

320
00:27:58,160 --> 00:28:00,240
But why don't I see her?

321
00:28:00,400 --> 00:28:01,240
It's already the You period.

322
00:28:01,960 --> 00:28:02,319
Maybe...

323
00:28:02,519 --> 00:28:04,400
Maybe she's delayed.

324
00:28:05,200 --> 00:28:06,079
Lady Zhen,

325
00:28:06,839 --> 00:28:08,799
about Lady Su's injuries...

326
00:28:09,119 --> 00:28:09,559
Well...

327
00:28:09,799 --> 00:28:11,880
Don't overthink it.

328
00:28:21,599 --> 00:28:22,720
With her status,

329
00:28:23,480 --> 00:28:25,319
no one would dare to mistreat her.

330
00:28:26,279 --> 00:28:27,200
If there's any trouble,

331
00:28:27,799 --> 00:28:28,839
and if I can help,

332
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:30,680
I'll do my best.

333
00:30:34,359 --> 00:30:35,200
Your family

334
00:30:35,200 --> 00:30:36,920
ruined mine.

335
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:38,400
If you can't

336
00:30:38,400 --> 00:30:40,039
pay back by March,

337
00:30:42,319 --> 00:30:43,519
you know

338
00:30:43,960 --> 00:30:45,559
what I'll do.

339
00:30:46,279 --> 00:30:46,960
I know you

340
00:30:47,440 --> 00:30:49,000
hold a grudge against us.

341
00:30:49,599 --> 00:30:51,079
But for the sake of our past,

342
00:30:51,759 --> 00:30:52,920
could you give me and my family

343
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:53,680
another chance?

344
00:30:55,920 --> 00:30:56,240
My Lord.

345
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:02,200
What's up?

346
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:03,400
The clerk from Ren'an Hall came to report

347
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:04,759
that a madman came to the shop,

348
00:31:05,119 --> 00:31:06,319
causing a huge scene.

349
00:31:06,599 --> 00:31:07,119
The owner

350
00:31:07,119 --> 00:31:08,000
doesn't know what to do.

351
00:31:08,200 --> 00:31:09,000
Please come and decide.

352
00:31:13,599 --> 00:31:14,000
Stop!

353
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:14,799
Stop!

354
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:17,319
My herbs!

355
00:31:18,839 --> 00:31:19,480
Go!

356
00:31:26,240 --> 00:31:27,119
The madman is eating people!

357
00:31:27,480 --> 00:31:28,119
Shut up!

358
00:31:28,759 --> 00:31:29,200
Madman!

359
00:31:38,839 --> 00:31:39,160
Amazing!

360
00:31:39,799 --> 00:31:40,400
Amazing!

361
00:31:41,519 --> 00:31:42,720
So many healers have come,

362
00:31:42,720 --> 00:31:43,480
yet they were all helpless.

363
00:31:43,960 --> 00:31:45,079
With just one needle,

364
00:31:45,519 --> 00:31:47,640
she calmed the madman down!

365
00:32:03,400 --> 00:32:04,359
How did I get here?

366
00:32:04,799 --> 00:32:05,599
What happened?

367
00:32:06,119 --> 00:32:07,480
Your phlegm turbidity obstructs the heart,

368
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:08,960
causing liver fire to flare up,

369
00:32:09,839 --> 00:32:10,960
leading to mental derangement.

370
00:32:12,079 --> 00:32:12,680
Take this for seven days.

371
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:14,440
Avoid spicy foods and anger.

372
00:32:15,039 --> 00:32:15,799
Stay calm and rest.

373
00:32:16,599 --> 00:32:17,039
Healer,

374
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:19,880
you are truly a living Hua Tuo!

375
00:32:20,359 --> 00:32:20,720
Thank you!

376
00:32:21,119 --> 00:32:22,599
Thank you!

377
00:32:23,279 --> 00:32:24,079
Thank you, healer!

378
00:32:24,440 --> 00:32:25,480
Thank you, healer!
